                <p>
                    <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> is an open-source Bitcoin hardware wallet and tool kit that runs directly from a USB drive. By booting it on your existing PC, it bypasses your computer's host OS to create a secure, air-gapped cold storage solution—providing a powerful alternative to traditional Bitcoin hardware wallets.
