                <h2 class="section-heading">Repurpose, Don't Replace</h2>
                <p>
                    Stop squinting at tiny screens. By using a full-size display and keyboard, <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> makes it easy to clearly read and double-check every detail of your transaction before you approve it. It turns the computer you already own into a powerful, highly secure Bitcoin wallet—no extra gadgets required.
                </p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.75rem 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.65rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); background: var(--surface);">
                    <li style="font-size: 0.93rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5;"><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Runs on any x86 laptop or desktop using a standard 4GB+ USB drive.  Supports most internal webcams or external cameras.</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 0.93rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5;"><strong>Hardened Isolation:</strong> Complete hardware isolation with all networking, internal SSD access, and non-essential peripherals strictly disabled upon boot.</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 0.93rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5;"><strong>Encrypted Persistence:</strong> Secure, password-protected storage featuring a streamlined, mobile-integrated unlock via QR code.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    <strong>SafeKeepVault</strong> bypasses your host operating system to initialize a hardened, offline environment directly from the USB drive. By strictly isolating the system from the internet, internal storage, and unnecessary drivers, it ensures your private data never leaves the USB drive. Once the system is shut down, the memory is completely purged leaving no trace of your private keys or your activities.
                </p>
